quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  28,60,Kandi icyo mwahawe cyose ni umunezero w’ubuzima bw’isi n’umutako wayo (by’igihe gito). Naho ibiri kwa Allah (ingororano) ni byo byiza kandi bizahoraho. Ese ntimugira ubwenge
  28,61,"Ese uwo twasezeranyije isezerano ryiza (ijuru) maze akazaribona, ni kimwe n’uwo twahaye umunezero w’ubuzima bw’isi (akaba ari bwo ahitamo gusa) maze ku munsi w’imperuka akazaba mu bazazanwa (ngo bahanwe)"
  28,62,Kandi (wibuke) umunsi (Allah) azabahamagara akavuga ati “Ese ibyo mwajyaga mumbangikanya na byo biri he?”
  28,63,Ba bandi bazahamwa n’imvugo (y’ibihano) bazavuga bati “Nyagasani! Bariya ni abo twayobeje. Twabayobeje nk’uko natwe twayobye. Turabihakanye imbere yawe! Rwose si twe basengaga.”
  28,64,"Bazabwirwa bati “Ngaho nimuhamagare ibigirwamana byanyu! Maze babihamagare ariko ntibizabitaba. Nuko babone ibihano (bibategereje), maze (bicuze bavuga bati): Iyo tuza kuba twarayobotse.”"
  28,65,Kandi (wibuke) umunsi (Allah) azabahamagara akavuga ati “Ni iki mwasubije Intumwa (ku byo twazibatumyeho)?”
  28,66,Bazabura icyo basubiza kuri uwo munsi kandi ntibazashobora kubazanya
  28,67,"Ariko uzaba yaricujije, akemera (Allah) akanakora ibikorwa byiza, uwo azaba mu bakiranutsi"
  28,68,"Kandi Nyagasani wawe arema icyo ashaka akanahitamo (uwo aha ubutumwa), nta mahitamo (abantu) babigiramo. Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya na byo"
  28,69,Ndetse Nyagasani wawe azi ibyo ibituza byabo bihishe n’ibyo bagaragaza
  28,70,"Kandi ni We Allah; nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri itari We. Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibye ku ntangiriro (ku isi) no ku mperuka. Ni we uca iteka, kandi iwe ni ho muzagarurwa"